file.name: capture.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.1.0

info:
  title: Capture results models
  version: ^0.0.0

components:
  schemas:
    Capture.Request:
      description: >-
        The capture result request to the traffic generator.
        Stops the port capture on the port_name and returns the capture.
      type: object
      required: [port_name]
      properties:
        port_name:
          description: >-
            The name of a port a capture is started on.
          type: string
          x-constraint:
          - '/components/schemas/Port/properties/name'
